We are looking for Mechanical Engineers and Industrial Designers to beta-test a new feature we've been working very hard on the past few weeks.

It will allow you to store, comment, and manage revisions of your CAD files. This is also connected to Jiga's base features like connection to suppliers and asking for real quotes for your part designs.

If you are interested in beta-testing, please comment or email me: yonatan@jiga.io

Yonatan.
